Air & Water Technologies Corp, dem complete di acquisition of Falcon Associates Inc, Bristol, Pa, asbestos Abiram, for $25 million stock.

Air & Water, wey dey provide environmental services, and systems, dem pay about 1.4 million of wetin be Falcon own.

For American Stock Exchange (Economic Exchange) Friday, Air & Water bin close for one hour wey dem dey sell for $17.50.

For July 31 Air & Water do nearly 10 million share.

